window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Vale was born in battle 700 years ago, and in all this time, he's never encountered an enemy that poses a real challenge. Until now.</p> <p>Devi has been told terrifying tales of vengeful gods since her youth. She never thought that she would wake up in a world where she had to fight them.</p> <p>They're opposites: He gets on her nerves; she is under his skin, and if they're to survive, they must join forces.</p> <p><b>Disclaimer: </b></p> <p>Frostbound Throne is a trilogy. Each book is novel length. The story ends at the third book (cliffhanger warning). </p> <ul> <li><i>Song of Night, Book 1</i></li> <li><i>Song of Winter, Book 2</i></li> <li><i>Song of Heaven and Ice, Book 3 </i></li> </ul> <p> <i>Court of Sin is a series of adult fantasy novels unsuitable for clean listeners.</i></p>"; 
